summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting easements over a portion of the southwest one-quarter of Section 36, Township 24 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; a portion of Block 2, Steel Plant Addition; and a portion of the northeast one-quarter of Section 36, Township 24 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; for storm drain, sanitary sewer and street purposes.
